<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Discount Approval Request</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 850px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .email-container {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b 0%, #ee5a24 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 25px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        .header::before {
            content: "‚ö†Ô∏è";
            position: absolute;
            left: 30px;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .urgency-banner {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            margin: 0;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #856404;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        .request-summary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e3f2fd 0%, #f3e5f5 100%);
            border: 1px solid #bbdefb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            position: relative;
        }
        .request-summary::before {
            content: "üìä";
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .request-summary h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #1565c0;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .opportunity-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .details-header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .details-grid {
            padding: 20px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        .detail-item {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .detail-item:last-child,
        .detail-item:nth-last-child(2) {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #495057;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .detail-value {
            color: #212529;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        .amount-highlight {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #28a745, #20c997);
            color: white;
            padding: 3px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .discount-highlight {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #dc3545, #fd7e14);
            color: white;
            padding: 3px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .justification-section {
            background-color: #fff8e1;
            border: 1px solid #ffecb3;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .justification-section h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #f57f17;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .justification-text {
            background-color: white;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 15px;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #424242;
            min-height: 60px;
        }
        .approval-actions {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f5e8 0%, #f0f8ff 100%);
            border: 2px solid #28a745;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .approval-actions h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #155724;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .action-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .btn {
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .btn-approve {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745, #20c997);
            color: white;
        }
        .btn-reject {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc3545, #fd7e14);
            color: white;
        }
        .btn-review {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007bff, #6610f2);
            color: white;
        }
        .deadline-warning {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .deadline-warning strong {
            color: #721c24;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .submitter-info {
            background-color: #e7f3ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #007bff;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6c757d;
            border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        .signature {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 2px solid #e9ecef;
            color: #495057;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            body {
                padding: 10px;
            }
            .content {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .details-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 10px;
            }
            .action-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
            .btn {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 200px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Discount Approval Required</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="urgency-banner">
            üïê Action Required - Approval Deadline: {!Opportunity.CloseDate}
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Dear <strong>User</strong>,
            </div>
            
            <div class="request-summary">
                <h3>Approval Request Summary</h3>
                <p><strong>{!Opportunity.OwnerFullName}</strong> has submitted the following opportunity for discount approval. Your review and decision are required to proceed with this deal.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="opportunity-details">
                <div class="details-header">
                    üíº Opportunity Details
                </div>
                <div class="details-grid">
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Opportunity Name</div>
                        <div class="detail-value"><strong>{!Opportunity.Name}</strong></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Account</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{!Opportunity.Account}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Original Amount</div>
                        <div class="detail-value"><span class="amount-highlight">{!Opportunity.Amount}</span></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Requested Discount</div>
                        <div class="detail-value"><span class="discount-highlight">{!Opportunity.Discount_Percent__c}%</span></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Discounted Amount</div>
                        <div class="detail-value"><span class="amount-highlight">{!Opportunity.Discounted_Amount__c}</span></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Expected Close Date</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{!Opportunity.CloseDate}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Current Stage</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{!Opportunity.StageName}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Lead Source</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{!Opportunity.LeadSource}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Competition</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{!Opportunity.Campaign}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="justification-section">
                <h3>üìù Business Justification</h3>
                <div class="justification-text">
                    {!Opportunity.Discount_Justification__c}
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="submitter-info">
                <strong>Submitted by:</strong> {!Opportunity.OwnerFullName}<br>
                <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:{!Opportunity.OwnerEmail}">{!Opportunity.OwnerEmail}</a><br>
                <strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:{!Opportunity.OwnerPhone}">{!Opportunity.OwnerPhone}</a><br>
                <strong>Submission Date:</strong> {!TODAY()}
            </div>
            
            <div class="deadline-warning">
                <strong>‚è∞ Approval Required By: {!Opportunity.CloseDate}</strong><br>
                <small>Please review and provide your decision to avoid delays in the sales process.</small>
            </div>
            
            <div class="approval-actions">
                <h3>üéØ Take Action</h3>
                <p>To approve or reject this discount request, please take one of the following actions:</p>
                
                <div class="action-buttons">
                    <a href="{!Opportunity.Link}" class="btn btn-approve">‚úÖ Approve Request</a>
                    <a href="{!Opportunity.Link}" class="btn btn-reject">‚ùå Reject Request</a>
                    <a href="{!Opportunity.Link}" class="btn btn-review">üëÄ Review in Salesforce</a>
                </div>
                
                <p><small><strong>Note:</strong> Click "Review in Salesforce" to access the full opportunity record, add comments, or view additional details before making your decision.</small></p>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background-color: #d1ecf1; border: 1px solid #bee5eb; border-radius: 6px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <p><strong>Questions or Need More Information?</strong><br>
                Contact {!Opportunity.OwnerFullName} directly at <a href="mailto:{!Opportunity.OwnerEmail}">{!Opportunity.OwnerEmail}</a> or reach out to the Sales Operations team for assistance.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="signature">
                <p><strong>Best regards,</strong><br>
                Salesforce Approval System<br>
                {!Organization.Name}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            This approval request was automatically generated by Salesforce on {!TODAY()}<br>
            Please do not reply to this email directly. Use the action buttons above or contact the opportunity owner.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>